    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>A shape-walker agent of the Pale Maw — a spy trained in the art of wyrd-bound transformation to assume the forms of others. This agent is less powerful than Dreyfus himself, deployed on reconnaissance and infiltration missions where plausible deniability matters. Their wyrd-claw strikes leave psychic echoes that cloud memory, and their Hollowing Gaze can read surface thoughts. When cornered, they shift form and flee — the Escape Protocol is their signature.</p>",
